Subject: {{group.name}} collective {{month}} report

{{> header}}

<style>

h1 {
  font-weight:normal;
}

h2 {
  margin-top: 30px;
  color:#75cc1f;
  font-weight:normal;
}

ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
}

ul li {
  margin: 5px 0px;
}
.counter {
  font-size: 36px;
  color: #7FADF2;
}
.delta {
  color: #7A7B82;
}
.label {

}
.reimbursed {
  color: #7A7B82;
}
</style>

<div style="font-size:10pt">

<h1>{{group.name}} {{month}} report</h1>

<p>Hi there! This your monthly report for your open collective with your latest balance (as of the last day of last month) and all the expenses that were submitted.
 Don't hesitate to send us your feedback by replying to this email. You can always visit your collective page to get the latest up to date data: <a href="{{group.publicUrl}}">{{group.publicUrl}}</a></p>

<p>You've probably seen some changes to your collective already, we'd like to tell you more about them! See the #changelog at the bottom of this email.</p> 

<center>
<table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=300 style="margin: 30px 0px">
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="counter">{{{currency group.balance currency=group.currency}}}</span></td>
    <td width=200>&nbsp;</td>
    <td align="center"><span class="counter">{{group.backersCount}}</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="label">current balance</span></td>
    <td></td>
    <td align="center" nowrap><span class="label">total backers</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center"><span class="delta">({{{sign group.balanceDelta}}}{{{currency group.balanceDelta currency=group.currency}}})</span></span></td>
    <td></td>
    <td align="center"><span class="delta">({{{sign group.backersCountDelta}}}{{group.backersCountDelta}})</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br />
<a href="{{group.publicUrl}}#backers"><img src="{{group.publicUrl}}/backers.png?avatarHeight=48&maxWidth=600&button=false&order=recent" /></a>
<a href="{{group.publicUrl}}#sponsors"><img src="{{group.publicUrl}}/sponsors.png?avatarHeight=48&maxWidth=600&button=false&order=recent" /></a>
</center>

<h2>Expenses</h2>
<table width="100%" border=0>

{{#each group.expenses}}
  <tr>
    <td valign="top">{{{moment createdAt format="MM/DD"}}}</td>
    <td align="right" valign="top" nowrap>{{{currency netAmountInGroupCurrency currency=currency}}}</td>
    <td valign="top"><a href="{{@root.config.host.app}}/groups/{{@root.group.id}}/expenses/{{id}}">{{description}}</a></td>
    <td valign="top" class="{{toLowerCase status}}">{{toLowerCase status}}</td>
  </tr>
{{else}}
  No expense submitted. <a href="{{@root.group.publicUrl}}/expenses/new">Submit an expense</a>
{{/each}}
</table>

{{#if topBackers}}
<h2>Recent sponsor activity on Open Collective</h2>
<ul>
{{#each topBackers}}
  <li><a href="{{website}}">{{name}}</a> gave {{{donationsString}}}</li>
{{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

{{#if group.related}}
  <h2>Check out similar collectives</h2>
  <ul>
  {{#each group.related}}
    <li><a href="{{publicUrl}}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport">{{name}}</a>, on a mission to {{mission}} [<a href="{{publicUrl}}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport#support">support them!</a>]</li>
  {{/each}}
  </ul>
{{/if}}

<h2>Featured collective</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://opencollective.com/ubie?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport">UBIE Network</a>: We are on a mission to get Unconditional Basic Income (UBI) introduced in Europe. [<a href="https://opencollective.com/ubie?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=monthlyreport#support">support that mission!</a>]</li>
</ul>

