<h2>Changelog</h2>
<ul>

<li><b>Editable Collective</b> Woohooo You can log in through your collective, hover over logo, mission and texts to modify. Also access your profile from the dropdown menu. We are still working on hero image and adding contributors.</li>

<li><b>Counter</b> We tried to remove the counter with the yearly budget but many of you were missing it. So it's back and we've added the total number of people that contribute to your collective (that includes your core contributors, your backers, your sponsors and your contributors on github if you have attached a github repository to your collective)</li>

<li><b>Why Join Section</b> The black section in the middle is going away soon. You'll be able to use markdown to create any title and content in the long description as well as use it to show images and video.</li>

<li><b>Support</b> We now have an dedicated email for requests (support@opencollective.com) as well as the <a href="https://slack.opencollective.com">#user-feedback channel in slack</a></li>

<li><b>Twitter</b> You can now link your collective to your twitter account to automatically thank your backers/sponsors. <a href="{{group.publicUrl}}/connect/twitter">Deets here</a> (it's still a bit ugly but it works!)</li>

<li><b>Slack</b> Don't forget to send Pia (pia@opencollective.com) your slack webhook url if you'd like to receive notifications for new donations/expenses in your slack channel.</li>

</ul>

</div>

{{> footer}}